         <property name="html">
          <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Microsoft YaHei UI'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#129e30;&quot;&gt;本软件完全免费，任何收费皆为诈骗。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700; color:#ff0000;&quot;&gt;严禁倒卖！严禁倒卖！严禁倒卖！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;安装完成后打开游戏进入主菜单才可打开配置界面！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;默认配置界面地址：&lt;a href=&quot;http://127.0.0.1:58744&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; text-decoration: underline; color:#00aaff;&quot;&gt;http://127.0.0.1:58744&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;提示：配置修改后可通过断线重连（如果开启了快捷键可按Ctrl+D）尝试使其生效（如修改了宠物）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;hsmod修改的宠物无法互动。酒馆四选一已失效，如解锁后选旁边2个角色会卡在选角色界面，时间结束后会随机选中间2个之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
